[{"id":"VR255375","type":"longtextV2","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"direction_paragraph\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"><strong>Directions: Write a coherent and well-organized response IN SPANISH on the topic that appears below.</strong></p>\n\n<p class=\"direction_paragraph\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"><strong>Instrucciones: Escribe una respuesta coherente y bien organizada EN ESPAÑOL sobre el siguiente tema.</strong></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"complex_stimulus\">\n<div class=\"prompt\">Lee la siguiente selección y estudia la pintura. Luego compara la representación de la construcción del género en las dos obras en relación con la primera mitad del siglo XX.</div>\n\n<div class=\"prompt\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div class=\"stimulus_block\">\n<div class=\"passage\">\n<div class=\"poetry style:1\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<p class=\"title_line passage-title\">A Julia de Burgos</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"verse text-center\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>[...]</span></div>\n\n<div class=\"verse text-center\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Tú eres dama casera, resignada, sumisa,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>atada a los prejuicios de los hombres; yo no;</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>que yo soy Rocinante corriendo desbocado</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>olfateando horizontes de justicia de Dios.</span></div>\n\n<div class=\"verse text-center\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Tú en ti misma no mandas; a ti todos te mandan;</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>en ti mandan tu esposo, tus padres, tus parientes,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>el cura, la modista, el teatro, el casino,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>el auto, las alhajas, el banquete, el champán,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>el cielo y el infierno, y el qué dirán social.</span></div>\n\n<div class=\"verse text-center\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>[...]</span></div>\n\n<div class=\"verse text-center\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Tú, clavada al estático dividendo ancestral,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>y yo, un uno en la cifra del divisor social,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>somos el duelo a muerte que se acerca fatal.</span></div>\n\n<div class=\"verse text-center\"><span class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Cuando las multitudes corran alborotadas</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>dejando atrás cenizas de injusticias quemadas,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>y cuando con la tea de las siete virtudes,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>tras los siete pecados, corran las multitudes,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>contra ti, y contra todo lo injusto y lo inhumano,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\" style=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>yo iré en medio de ellas con la tea en la mano.</span></div>\n<span class=\"mandatory_credit_block\"><span style=\"font-size:0.8em;\"><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">Julia de Burgos</span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">“A Julia de Burgos”</span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic\">Poema en veinte surcos</span></span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">Used by permission of Ediciones Huracán.</span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">(Originalmente se publicó en 1939).</span></span></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"stimulus_block\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents a painting. In the painting, a woman is holding a flag in one hand and the scales of justice in the other hand. A lion is shown next to her along with a shield that contains the inscription: libertad, igualdad, fraternidad.\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VR255375.g01.png\" width=\"400\" /><span class=\"mandatory_credit_block\"><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic\">Alegoría de la República, la Segunda República Española (1931-1936)</span>; póster publicado en Valencia en 1931.</span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">Heritage Image Partnership Ltd / Alamy Stock Photo</span></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n","rubricRef":"VR255375_rubric"}]